OL,3,CFarmer against Center Parcs believes
OL,4,Cit'll harm rural life
OL,6,FA farmer against plans to build a
OL,7,FCenter Parcs in the Scottish Borders
OL,8,Fbelieves the site will harm rural life.
OL,10,FBosses behind the scheme say the #400m
OL,11,Fholiday park will create more than
OL,12,F1,200 jobs, transforming leisure and
OL,13,Ftourism in the area.
OL,15,FCenter Parcs first outlined its vision
OL,16,Fto people in the Scottish Borders last
OL,17,FNovember. The company submitted its
OL,18,Fplanning application for 700 holiday
OL,19,Flodges, located three miles north of
OL,20,FHawick, last month.
