OL,3,CFarmer against Center Parcs believes
OL,4,Cit'll harm rural life
OL,6,FMerlin Lewis's land will be located
OL,7,Fnext to the proposed site. He said:
OL,8,F"We are going to be fenced in by a
OL,9,Fstructure that more closely resembles
OL,10,Fa prison enclosure than anything that
OL,11,Fwould divide rural land parcels.
OL,13,F"The nature of the barrier itself,
OL,14,Fwhich Center Parcs are referring to,
OL,15,Fis bunding, which is a very
OL,16,Fsubstantial earth mound, and then a
OL,17,Fmetal impenetrable fence. More along
OL,18,Fthe lines of what you'd expect around,
OL,19,Fan electrical station or something
OL,20,Fwhere security was needed."
