OL,3,CFarmer against Center Parcs believes
OL,4,Cit'll harm rural life
OL,6,FThe holiday company says there have
OL,7,Fbeen four objections so far from a
OL,8,Ftotal of almost 50 people, who have
OL,9,Fraised concerns.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Center Parcs says
OL,12,Fthe business is familiar with ensuring
OL,13,Fits sites do not impact farming
OL,14,Foperations in the UK and Ireland.
OL,16,FThey said: "Before submitting our
OL,17,Fplanning application, we engaged with
OL,18,Fmore than 1,000 members of the public
OL,19,Fover eight months, with that feedback
OL,20,Fshaping and refining our proposals.
