OL,4,Cit'll harm rural life
OL,6,F"We also held dedicated meetings with
OL,7,Fthose living and working closest to
OL,8,Fthe site, listening carefully to
OL,9,Fconcerns around lodge positioning,
OL,10,Fscreening and access, and making
OL,11,Fchanges to our initial plans as a
OL,12,Fresult.
OL,14,F"In addition, we invited immediate
OL,15,Fneighbours to visit our existing
OL,16,Fvillages to see first-hand how we
OL,17,Foperate and how we work alongside
OL,18,Flocal communities.
