OL,6,F"As part of the planning process, we
OL,7,Fhave carried out detailed assessments
OL,8,Fon issues such as transport, water
OL,9,Fsupply and noise, working closely with
OL,10,Fthe relevant authorities.
OL,12,F"These assessments are now being
OL,13,Freviewed by public bodies, including
OL,14,FTransport Scotland and Scottish Water,
OL,15,Fbefore a decision is taken by Scottish
OL,16,FBorders Council in due course.
