OL,6,F"Should our application be approved,
OL,7,Fwe are fully committed to maintaining
OL,8,Fan open and constructive dialogue with
OL,9,Four neighbours and the wider
OL,10,Fcommunity, and to continue building
OL,11,Fpositive, long-term relationships."
OL,13,FAnother nearby farmer, Peter
OL,14,FPitchford, said: "They will have a
OL,15,Fwater treatment plant, which will
OL,16,Fdischarge not clean water but treated
OL,17,Fwater, which will then be put into the
OL,18,FTeviot, either by tanker or by
OL,19,Fpipeline.
