OL,6,F"It's not unclear, but that water will
OL,7,Fstill have contaminants in it.
OL,8,FChlorine from the public area, bathing
OL,9,Fplaces and also salt off the road."
OL,11,FMerlin Lewis added: "I completely
OL,12,Fdisagree with the economic impact that
OL,13,Fthis has been set out. I think that it
OL,14,Fis shortsighted and hasn't properly
OL,15,Fconsidered who will be employed and in
OL,16,Fwhat capacity, and what broader
OL,17,Feconomic benefit will actually be born
OL,18,Fout, rather than something that's been
OL,19,Fwritten in a very optimistic way and
OL,20,Fhasn't been properly scrutinised.
